<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>bug containing revision: 11362</p>

<p>You'll still get errors on uploading files with Zend_Form_Element_File although the field is not required. The cause of the problem is, that the line 162 in Zend_Form_Element_File.php $adapter-&gt;setOptions(array('ignoreNoFile' =&gt; true)); does not take effect.</p>

<p>Solution: (Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract class on line 476)</p>

<p>old:
$this-&gt;_options += $options;</p>

<p>fixed:
$this-&gt;_options = $options + $this-&gt;_options;</p>

